{"tid":1797774,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好當港超係CONDOM","createTime":"2019-12-25T16:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T06:13:18.000Z","uid":208122,"like":27,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2ef1d6ed7f1f9698d9da05a4c45d5ecf5595fe2b","tid":1797774,"uid":208122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:46:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">高級銀牌準決賽 <span style=\"color: gold;\">理文</span> Vs <strong><span style=\"color: green;\">大埔</span></strong></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n香港人撐完港足，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好當港超係CONDOM</span>。<br />\n一定要出錢出力入場撐港超，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復足球文化圈</span><br />\n成日話假日香港冇地方好去冇野好做，依家就同我入場<br />\n淨係需要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">$30</span></span>就入場睇到<br />\n<br />\n理文對和富大埔 高級銀牌準決賽<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期四12月26日 下午4:00<br />\n旺角大球場<br />\n$30特惠，$80正常票價</strong></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n光復香港由重建港足文化開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFKDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=de07aedf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YH3YWg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYH3YWg6.jpg&h=7b41ee30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bee6081e8b7b3937216b68b1089b1f959b1e853e","tid":1797774,"uid":114252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:48:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba4420f8d655c067df6995f9e07d4b1a0901b402","tid":1797774,"uid":340221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:57:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"975cf013a0defb67bf6f64cc5fe627acde17ad9c","tid":1797774,"uid":78060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:23:21